<dl id="n42026f"> <dt class="nbunit"><a name="n42" href="#n42026f">N42 (VI.B.31)</a>:  <a href="../../ff/fnbs/n42all.htm#n42026f"> 26(f)</a></dt> <dd> <blockquote> 1215 Lateran</blockquote> <dd class="well"> <blockquote class="sources">It is a public fact, which no learned Roman Catholic has ever denied, that auricular confession became a dogma and obligatory practice of the Church only at the Council of Lateran in the year 1215, under the Pope Innocent III. <small> Chiniquy, <a name="CPWC" href="../../ff/fdra/fdex.htm#CPWC"><cite title="source">The Priest The Woman and The Confessional</cite></a> (n.d.) 128</small></blockquote> </dd></dl>
